            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>763</offset>
                <text>He did not have macrocephaly at 12 months during the initial evaluation as his head circumference (HC) was 46.5 cm (50th centile) and 49.5 cm at 36 months (50th centile).</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>934</offset>
                <text>Karyotype was normal 46,XY and Smith Lemli Opitz syndrome was ruled out with normal levels of 7 and 8 dehydrocholesterol from blood spots.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1073</offset>
                <text>His echocardiogram was normal.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1104</offset>
                <text>Direct sequencing of the KIF7 gene identified a homozygous T to C substitution at the donor splice site of intron 3 c.529+2T&gt;C.</text>
            </sentence>
            <sentence>
                <offset>1232</offset>
                <text>Sequencing of parents confirmed that they are both heterozygous for this mutation.</text>
            </sentence>
